  severity: low
  comment: |
    Of 146 `unsafe` occurrences across src/, only 19 lines contain a
    `// SAFETY:` comment. bytes.rs (~1670 LoC, 55 unsafe occurrences)
    has zero `SAFETY:` comments — every vtable dispatch block (e.g.
    lines 339, 515, 563, 664, 683, 690, 1044, 1057) and every internal
    raw-pointer arithmetic block (e.g. 406, 672) is uncommented. The
    invariants are real (vtable contract, offset-within-buffer) and
